Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.305
How can we have CloudFront fail over to a different AWS region?
我们如何将 CloudFront 故障转移到不同的 AWS 区域?

00:00:04.305 --> 00:00:08.115
In order to automatically failover to a different AWS region,
为了自动故障转移到不同的 AWS 区域 

00:00:08.115 --> 00:00:10.830
we should use CloudFront's origin groups.
我们应该使用 CloudFront的原始组 

00:00:10.830 --> 00:00:14.520
This will allow CloudFront to decide if it should follow
这将允许 CloudFront 决定是否应该遵循

00:00:14.520 --> 00:00:20.160
a primary S3 bucket or failover to a secondary S3 bucket based on the availability.
基于可用性的主 S3 存储区或故障转移到辅助 S3 存储区 

00:00:20.160 --> 00:00:23.040
We could use multiple distributions or
我们可以使用多个分布

00:00:23.040 --> 00:00:26.175
multiple origins within our CloudFront distribution,
我们的 CloudFront 分布中的多个起源 

00:00:26.175 --> 00:00:27.705
but this would still require
但这还需要

00:00:27.705 --> 00:00:32.170
manual intervention to actually cut these over in a DR event.
手动干预以在 DR 事件中实际剪切这些事件 
